# Naming Consistency (Critical)

- Use consistent semantic naming across the project:
  - `primary`
  - `background`
  - `text`
  - `muted`
- Do NOT introduce alternative names for the same concept (avoid synonyms).
  - Example: if `primary` exists, do not create `brandPrimary`, `main`, or `accentPrimary`.
- When adding new semantic tokens later, define one canonical name and reuse it everywhere.

